venue.name: The MGM Grand Theater at Foxwoods Resort Casino

description: We want to celebrate the release of our upcoming album "Hail to the King" with you all by playing a free show at the legendary Hollywood Palladium on the eve of its release. Follow the instructions below and get your free tickets to join us August 26th for this monumental occasion! See you there!Fans will be able to obtain tickets for this free show from a few places around Los Angeles and Orange Counties. There is a one ticket per person limit and tickets are non-transferable.1. Beginning Monday, August 19, fans can tune into KROQ and listen for their chance to win.2. On August 22nd fans can obtain tickets from two locations in Orange County. Lineups start at 3pm, with tickets being given away at 4pm. A very limited quantity of tickets will be available on a first come first serve basis.Locations:Slide Bar122 E Commonwealth AvenueFullerton, CA 92832AndJohnny’s Saloon17428 Beach BlvdHuntington Beach, CA 926473. On Friday, August 23,2013 tickets will be available at the Hollywood Palladium Box office. Lineup starts at 3pm, with tickets being given away at 5pm.****** NOTE: YOU WILL NOT BE ALLOWED TO LINE UP PRIOR TO 3PM
